These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, indonesian, british
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the german is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the british is between the german and the indonesian##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| Nationality     | french     | indonesian | british  | german      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, water-polo, cycling
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Sport     | ice-hockey    | water-polo | rowing | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, orange, fuchsia
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person who likes orange is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| Color           | chestnut | fuchsia | orange | ivory  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, techno, disco, funk
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the fan of disco##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | dubstep   | funk  | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Birthday      | april | may | december       | january |

