.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, country, salsa, metal
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the fan of salsa is between the fan of metal and the person drinking juice##2
3. the fan of pop is between the fan of salsa and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | country | pop  | salsa    | metal  |

