.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, tram, ship
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, scientific, superhero
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the ship is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Transport         | ship | tram | scooter | helicopter   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific | horror      | superhero |

