.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, horse, snake
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, romance, musical, time-travel
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the fish is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching mystery movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish   | horse      | snake      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | musical | mystery | time-travel |

