.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, purple, orange, lilac
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, russian
1. the argentine is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the person who likes orange is between the russian and the chinese##2
3. the person who likes purple is the chinese##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Color   | grey | purple | orange      | lilac   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | chinese    | argentine | russian |

