2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Color   | aquamarine     | ivory  | turquise | orange |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | turtle | hamster     | rat    |

