.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, billiard, mah-jongg
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
5. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Game   | monopoly | billiard  | mah-jongg | canasta |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

