3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| House   | cape-cod  | cottage | craftsman  | ranch-style      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

