6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | dancing | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | adventure       | family   | martial-arts      |

